The '''Skullsmashers''' were a tribe of unusually strong and fierce [[ogre]]s who made their base in [[Fangjaws Hold]] in [[Thar]]. They were known to enslave "lesser" neighbors such as [[goblin]]s and even [[human]]s and [[dwarves]], working them hard, usually to death in just a few months.{{cite web|url=http://www.wizards.com/DnD/Article.aspx?x=dnd/drrl/20071217a|title=The Tribes of Thar|accessdate=2007-12-21|author=[[Richard Baker]]|date=2007-12-17|work=Realmslore|publisher=[[Wizards of the Coast]]}}
